Tuxedo atmi++ v2.1 (herbert.koelman@me.com)
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Relese 2.1 (beta) of the atmi++ library. It has been mostly tested on Linux 
C6 using Tuxedo. Some basic testings have been done on AIX 5.3 again 
with Tuxedo.

To use in your project you will need :
- content of include/ directory.
- content of lib/ directory
- link your code with -latmi++ and -latmiutl++

Bugs can be reported at issues@atmiplusplus.projects.dev2dev.bea.com

